tables.name: users
tables.schema:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `users` (
  `id` bigint(16) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `type` varchar(32) NOT NULL,
  `author` bigint(16) DEFAULT NULL,
  `data` json DEFAULT NULL,
  `private` json DEFAULT NULL,
  `url` longtext,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1

tables.name: user_relationships
tables.schema:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `user_relationships` (
  `id` bigint(16) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `type` varchar(32) NOT NULL,
  `author` bigint(16) NOT NULL,
  `subject` bigint(16) DEFAULT NULL,
  `data` json DEFAULT NULL,
  `url` longtext,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `users_rel_author_fk` (`author`),
  KEY `users_rel_subject_fk` (`subject`),
  CONSTRAINT `users_rel_author_fk` FOREIGN KEY (`author`) REFERENCES `users` (`id`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE,
  CONSTRAINT `users_rel_subject_fk` FOREIGN KEY (`subject`) REFERENCES `users` (`id`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=31 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1

tables.name: resources

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `resources` (

) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=14 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1
